        options: ["She is non-adherent to her medication","Lamotrigine clearance increases by 50-100% during pregnancy due to estrogen-induced glucuronidation, and her dose needs to be increased","The lab result is erroneous and should be repeated","Pregnancy protects against seizures, so the seizure was not epilepsy-related"],
        correct: 1,
